ick, a small city just 20 minutes from downtown Columbus. This Community combines rural charm and hospitality with modern city conveniences. The Woods at Jefferson is a community filled with fun loving, active couple and families. where friends, and fun await!   Nearby attractions include: Easton Towne Center, shopping, dining and entertainment and more.  Quick Facts: - 3 Bedrooms - 2 Baths - 1,644 SF - WALKOUT Full Basement - Private Wooded .18 Acre Ravine Lot Backing to Reserve Space - Licking Heights School District ');
